### `crossdoor_nodes.h` / `crossdoor_nodes.cpp` — namespace `CrossDoor`

All functions are free functions; there are no class-based nodes in this file.

#### Free Functions

```cpp
BT::NodeStatus IsDoorOpen();
BT::NodeStatus IsDoorLocked();
BT::NodeStatus UnlockDoor();
BT::NodeStatus PassThroughDoor();
BT::NodeStatus PassThroughWindow();
BT::NodeStatus OpenDoor();
BT::NodeStatus CloseDoor();
void RegisterNodes(BT::BehaviorTreeFactory& factory);
```

**Door state** is held in two static file-scope booleans:
```cpp
static bool _door_open   = false;  // initial state: door closed
static bool _door_locked = true;   // initial state: door locked
```

These booleans are shared across all invocations of the CrossDoor functions within a single process. This is a deliberate simplification — the comment in the source explicitly notes that ports/blackboard are not used.

| Function | Behavior | Returns |
|---|---|---|
| `IsDoorOpen()` | Sleeps 500 ms; checks `_door_open`. | `SUCCESS` if open, `FAILURE` if closed. |
| `IsDoorLocked()` | Sleeps 500 ms; checks `_door_locked`. | `SUCCESS` if locked, `FAILURE` if unlocked. |
| `UnlockDoor()` | If locked, sleeps 2000 ms then sets `_door_locked = false`. | Always `SUCCESS`. |
| `PassThroughDoor()` | Sleeps 1000 ms. | `SUCCESS` if `_door_open`, else `FAILURE`. |
| `PassThroughWindow()` | Sleeps 1000 ms. | Always `SUCCESS`. |
| `OpenDoor()` | Returns `FAILURE` immediately if locked. Otherwise sleeps 2000 ms and sets `_door_open = true`. | `SUCCESS` or `FAILURE`. |
| `CloseDoor()` | If door is open, sleeps 1500 ms and sets `_door_open = false`. | Always `SUCCESS`. |

#### `RegisterNodes`

```cpp
void CrossDoor::RegisterNodes(BT::BehaviorTreeFactory& factory);
```

Registers all CrossDoor functions as simple conditions/actions:

| Registered Name | Kind |
|---|---|
| `"IsDoorOpen"` | SimpleCondition |
| `"PassThroughDoor"` | SimpleAction |
| `"PassThroughWindow"` | SimpleAction |
| `"OpenDoor"` | SimpleAction |
| `"CloseDoor"` | SimpleAction |
| `"IsDoorLocked"` | SimpleCondition |
| `"UnlockDoor"` | SimpleAction |

`BT_REGISTER_NODES(factory)` in `crossdoor_nodes.cpp` calls `CrossDoor::RegisterNodes(factory)`.

